{"tid":1359603,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"一人一信向律師會投訴何君堯","createTime":"2019-07-24T07:22:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-24T07:45:07.000Z","uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"b4da94c8d296bbbda42c022eaceb250058c7ed11","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:22:37.000Z","msg":"投訴何君堯律師<br />\n<br />\n2019年7月21日晚上，元朗發生多宗不明人士糾眾持械毆打市民事件，令多位市民包括孕婦以至記者受傷。<br />\n<br />\n期間，互聯網流傳多個片段，片段中，有酷似何君堯律師的人，答謝與懷疑毆打市民及記者有關人士，片段並獲傳媒廣範報道，令人懷疑何君堯律師與毆打事件有關。<br />\n<br />\n本人因此懷疑何君堯律師涉嫌違反《律師執業規則》1.01(d), 即「任何[事務]律師在執業為[事務]律師的過程中，不得作出...... 任何危及或損害或相當可能危及或損害...... 他的個人名譽或律師專業的名譽」。<br />\n<br />\n本人就此向 貴會作出投訴，懇請 貴會盡快調查及處理，以維護 貴會及事務律師的名譽。<br />\n<br />\n此致<br />\n香港律師會執業操守組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一人一信向律師會投訴何君堯<br />\n<br />\ncomplaints@hklawsoc.org.hk"},{"pid":"62a92c76fe7ac3d0ac3f88b760fdd2b2ce2ab4ea","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:22:48.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"1d6ddee4704146573a6ae549accdf8922431a0dd","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:22:58.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"d4601ad7fce155bbee1c97901c06faf3f30da41c","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:08.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"95a21f7eb12629acfef4e2bfc277ec00ce7835c6","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:18.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"c36b22c1f8b1165ce24ecb0e252012ad196d20a9","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"c27638cf53ff0bd2e7d64945ea4770ca8118d4b3","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"456f291018a0a3c57d34351ce1e2c50531fbcbfc","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:48.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"bf89283666f57199575b66a5c6c058408825d136","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:23:58.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"cd8dfaeebaeca915b192dd2e07a7079d42b641b6","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:24:11.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"061493f8b736ff35545e2077da1c964a437730ad","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"bf8e5f57ddd86ce86b1b84a0dcab14777731f2a9","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:25:51.000Z","msg":"11"},{"pid":"ba9017b450203370bf5de770d1d4587dac9be2f6","tid":1359603,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:43:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH <br />\n<br />\n唔好意思阻阻大家，我地想幫香港人出書，想收集大家意見<br />\n<br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"89522965b3d4419d9226bca6b966a5667abedd16","tid":1359603,"uid":100299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-24T07:45:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}